        <itunes:summary><![CDATA[What is your spiritual path like?  Some folks don't think they have one, but we all do.  Why is it that one way of going makes someone miserable while others going the same way seem so happy?

Religion is like underwear: what works well for one person might be totally inappropriate for someone else.

No preaching or "follow my way" here, but a way to find the doors and windows that you might like to peek through in finding your own path.

All spiritual paths are welcome here, although some might not like all of that personal responsibility!]]></itunes:summary>
