            <description><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-size: small;">It occurred to me that this would be a good time to have a celebration just for the sake of having a celebration. &nbsp;Just for the sake of seeing all that The Divine has done for us and giving some thanks, even if it isn't one of those marked-on-the-calendar appointed times for such a celebration.</span></p>
