<p><span style="font-size: small;">And, come to think of it, why not! &nbsp;And why not from time to time take a step back and look at the blessings you and I have and give some thanks. &nbsp;And who knows? &nbsp;Like in a retail business where it seems that the happy customer seems to get better service, in life it seems that people who give thanks wind up having more to give thanks about!</span></p>
