<p>If you want the full text of what the Universal Gnostic Fellowship teaches about The Law Of One, go to <a title="http://gnosticfellowship.com/one.html" href="http://gnosticfellowship.com/one.html">http://gnosticfellowship.com/one.html</a> and read that page.&nbsp; Here, I talk about applying it.</p>
