<p>I find that often the only way to get Christians' attention is to show that a point I am making is in their own scripture, and it is - abundantly.&nbsp; In fact, I don't even cite half of what I could cite.&nbsp; But there is a powerful promise and warning few seem to understand.&nbsp; What is ironic is that it is right next to a verse which is so often quoted that even atheists acknowledge it.&nbsp;</p>
